Yeah.
Alright,good luck, you two.

12:47.679 --> 12:48.855
You, too.
Yeah.
Alright. Yeah, yeah.

12:48.898 --> 12:49.943
Just do
what the kid said.

12:49.986 --> 12:53.250
We got to cut, pop,
shuck, husk...
Just --

12:53.294 --> 12:56.166
Mom...I don't --I don't think I can do it.

