13:28.590 --> 13:29.547
[ Grunts ]

13:29.591 --> 13:30.331
[ Screams ]

13:30.374 --> 13:31.506
[ Groans ] Ow.Jacob!

13:31.549 --> 13:32.289
Oooow!

13:35.379 --> 13:38.121
Ohh.Jacob. Oh, my God.
It's in your back.

13:38.165 --> 13:38.905
There's a sickle in your back.
Just get it out.

13:38.948 --> 13:40.254
Oh.
Is that okay?
Are you okay?

13:40.297 --> 13:42.734
Luckily, I, uh, had my mathtextbook with me today.

13:42.778 --> 13:43.997
Oh, wow.
That's a doozy.

13:44.040 --> 13:45.694
[ Laughs ] If it had beenmy grammar handouts,

13:45.737 --> 13:46.956
it could have
severed my spine.

13:47.000 --> 13:48.044
That would have sucked.

13:48.088 --> 13:50.525
I'm so sorry.
I am so sorry.Oh, it's okay.

13:50.568 --> 13:52.005
No. This got out of hand,

13:52.048 --> 13:54.224
and I just --
I'm so glad you're okay.

13:54.268 --> 13:55.269
