Mom, right?

13:55.312 --> 13:57.097
We feel awful.Uh, yeah, yeah, yeah.

13:57.140 --> 13:59.099
We feel terrible.We're so sorry --
We were just harvesting.

13:59.142 --> 14:01.014
No. No, we could have
really hurt him.

14:01.057 --> 14:03.233
Mom, this --
It's gone too far.

14:03.277 --> 14:05.148
Oh, come on.
There's no such thing.Oh, really?

14:05.192 --> 14:07.455
So, it's not too far
that you got intel from Connie

14:07.498 --> 14:09.109
that there was a harvest,
and all of a sudden,

14:09.152 --> 14:10.719
y-you're flying
1,500 miles out here

14:10.762 --> 14:12.155
so that we could
do it your way?

14:12.199 --> 14:13.896
I feel like this is my faultfor getting stabbed.

14:13.940 --> 14:15.680
Alright. Jacob, please don't
get involved here.

14:15.724 --> 14:17.508
I want you to be the best.
Is that so bad?

14:17.552 --> 14:19.684
Yes.
I don't need to be the best.

14:19.728 --> 14:21.599
Well, what kind of life
is that, Rio?

14:21.643 --> 14:23.079
[ Sighs ]I mean, are you
really satisfied

14:23.123 --> 14:24.689
with living in
a decrepit house

14:24.733 --> 14:28.171
and a decrepit farm
with nothing to show for it?

14:28.215 --> 14:31.174
