would not want this.

14:31.218 --> 14:33.046
I want this.

14:33.089 --> 14:34.612
I love my decrepit farm.

14:34.656 --> 14:36.397
I love my decrepit house.

14:36.440 --> 14:38.355
I am happier herejust trying to get by

14:38.399 --> 14:40.314
than I ever was in New York,trying to be the best.

14:40.357 --> 14:41.968
Okay.

14:42.011 --> 14:43.491
So, I get it.

14:43.534 --> 14:45.406
You just are happier
without me.

14:45.449 --> 14:47.495
I'm not --And you don't care
about me

14:47.538 --> 14:48.931
and you don't want me

14:48.975 --> 14:51.064
and I might as well
be dead.

14:51.107 --> 14:52.630
Okay?
I get it.

14:52.674 --> 14:54.937
Mom, that's not what I said.Mom, those were not my words.

14:54.981 --> 14:56.199
If you need me,
I'll be packing.

14:56.243 --> 14:57.722
