She's not answering.It's the silent treatment.

15:02.858 --> 15:04.207
Are you just gonna leave
the champagne

15:04.251 --> 15:05.426
and the snacks
right there?

15:05.469 --> 15:06.775
Mom?

15:06.818 --> 15:08.733
Constance: Rudy.

15:08.777 --> 15:10.779
I thought we had plans.

15:10.822 --> 15:12.346
We'll have to reschedule.

15:12.389 --> 15:13.738
I glued a circuit boardto my hand.

15:13.782 --> 15:15.653
Now I got a small currentgoing through my body.

15:15.697 --> 15:17.829
Things have never been better.This is so much fun.

15:17.873 --> 15:19.135
Really?

15:19.179 --> 15:20.832
