one thing,

15:20.876 --> 15:23.139
and your magnified eyes are
telling me a different story.

15:25.011 --> 15:26.795
You got to tell Brandonto back the hell off.

15:26.838 --> 15:28.318
Spoon men should be
hilarious and fun,

15:28.362 --> 15:30.625
not something that triesto kill you in the night.

15:30.668 --> 15:32.235
I'm so sorry, Rudy.

15:32.279 --> 15:34.020
I shouldn't have
forced him on you.

15:34.063 --> 15:37.066
I-I was so excited
about having him back, and --

15:37.110 --> 15:38.894
and now I don't know
what to do with him.

15:40.287 --> 15:43.029
When I came back from the army,I had no idea what to do.

15:43.072 --> 15:44.160
You come homeand, all of a sudden,

15:44.204 --> 15:46.032
no one's telling youwhere to be, what to wear.

15:46.075 --> 15:49.035
Took everything I hadto just take a break

15:49.078 --> 15:50.775
and do nothing
for a change.

15:50.819 --> 15:52.647
