because it's buffering,because our Wi-Fi is weak.

16:29.336 --> 16:31.077
No. You'reweak.
We're gonna do this.

16:31.120 --> 16:34.080
When I had Rio, the nurses
were completely useless.

16:34.123 --> 16:35.472
You know what I did?

16:35.516 --> 16:37.257
I reached up there,
and I delivered her myself.

16:37.300 --> 16:38.519
Give me the lubricant!

16:38.562 --> 16:41.304
Okay. The tutorial saysyou got to use olive oil.

16:41.348 --> 16:43.828
And you didn't spring
for extra virgin?We're on a budget!

16:43.872 --> 16:45.917
