world, and you get generic?

16:45.961 --> 16:47.702
You idiot!

16:47.745 --> 16:49.399
I-I-I got to say,there's something aboutwhen you yell at me

16:49.443 --> 16:51.836
that is mildly comforting,'cause it was -- it was weird

16:51.880 --> 16:53.055
when you were being nice to mewhen you first got here.

16:53.099 --> 16:54.535
'Cause I was faking it.

